# Anthropic API Key
# Get yours at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# Note: An admin must enable web search in the Anthropic Console first
# (Settings > Privacy > Web Search)
# Add to your shell profile (~/.zshrc, ~/.bashrc, ~/.bash_profile etc)
# or use a secrets manager (Doppler, 1Password CLI)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=${ANTHROPIC_API_KEY}
